CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1962, pg. A14 reads: "Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1962, pg. A14 reads: "...Chi Delta Mu supper dance, last Saturday at the Hilton..."
TitMainTitle: Five women, including from left: Toki Schalk Johnson, unknown woman, Winnie Nickens, and Winnie Ormes Houston, and five men, including possibly Leroy Randall, Jr., third from right, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
